{{藏傳佛教}}
'''慈克秋林仁波切'''（Tsikey Chokling Rinpoche）<ref>Urgyen, Tulku (2007), Blazing Splendor, Rangjung Yeshe Publications, p. xii, 362-3; {{ISBN|978-962-7341-56-7}}</ref>為[[藏傳佛教|藏傳佛教]][[寧瑪派|寧瑪派]]與[[噶舉派|噶舉派]]的[[金剛乘|金剛]][[上師|上師]]及作家。

慈克秋林仁波切由[[第十六世大寶法王|第十六世大寶法王]]認證為[[19世紀|19世紀]]著名[[伏藏師|伏藏師]][[秋吉林巴|秋吉林巴]]的第4世轉世，為秋林德薩傳承的持有者。<ref>[http://www.shedrub.org/teacherpage.php?tid=3 Ka-Nying Shedrup Ling Website] {{Webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150311043930/http://www.shedrub.org/teacherpage.php?tid=3 |date=2015-03-11 }}</ref><ref>Lama Kunsang, Lama Pemo, Marie Aubele and Jonathan C. Bell (Apr 16, 2012), History Of The Karmapas: The Odyssey Of The Tibetan Masters With The Black Crown, p. 269; {{ISBN|9781559393904}}</ref>慈克秋林仁波切出版有兩本著作。<ref>Rinpoche, Chokling (2008), The Great Gate: A Guidebook to the Guru's Heart Practice, Dispeller of All Obstacles, Rangjung Yeshe Publications. {{ISBN|962-7341-04-5}}.</ref><ref>Rinpoche, Chokling (2001), Lotus Ocean: Seeds of the Sublime Dharma, Rangjung Yeshe Publications.</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.rangjung.com/books/lotus-ocean.htm |title=Lotus Ocean from Rangjung Yeshe Publications |access-date=2020-12-22 |archive-date=2016-04-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160413163630/http://www.rangjung.com/books/lotus-ocean.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.rangjung.com/authors/Tsikey_Chokling_Rinpoche_interview.htm |title=Tsikey Chokling Rinpoche's Interview for Rabsel Tibetan Buddhist Magazine |access-date=2020-12-22 |archive-date=2016-03-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160303232102/http://www.rangjung.com/authors/Tsikey_Chokling_Rinpoche_interview.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.tricycle.com/feature/keys-happiness |title=Tricycle Magazine Interview with his son, Phakchok Rinpoche, mentioning Tsikey Chokling Rinpoche |access-date=2020-12-22 |archive-date=2016-03-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160315203157/http://www.tricycle.com/feature/keys-happiness |dead-url=no }}</ref>

慈克秋林仁波切的父親為[[大圓滿|大圓滿]]上師[[祖古烏金仁波切|祖古烏金仁波切]]，其弟子包括第十六世大寶法王。<ref>Doctor, Andreas (2013), Tibetan Treasure Literature: Revelation, Tradition, and Accomplishment in Visionary Buddhism, Snow Lion Publications, p. 12; {{ISBN|978-1559392365}}</ref><ref>Urgyen Tulku (2006), Quintessential Dzogchen: Confusion Dawns as Wisdom, Rangjung Yeshe Publications, p. 281-282, {{ISBN|9627341584}}.</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://cglf.org/our-lineage/kyabje-tsikey-chokling-rinpoche |title=Biography of Tsikey Chokling Rinpoche |access-date=2020-12-22 |archive-date=2015-02-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150209212238/http://cglf.org/our-lineage/kyabje-tsikey-chokling-rinpoche |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>Marcia Binder Schmidt (2002), The Dzogchen Primer: Embracing The Spiritual Path According To The Great Perfection. Shambhala Publications. p. 15 and 305, {{ISBN|1-57062-829-7}}.</ref> 慈克秋林仁波切的手足皆為金剛乘上師，長兄為[[秋吉尼瑪仁波切|秋吉尼瑪仁波切]]，胞弟有[[措尼仁波切|措尼仁波切]]與[[詠給明就仁波切|詠給明就仁波切]]。<ref>Rinpoche, Chokyi Nyima (2004), Union of Mahamudra and Dzogchen: A Commentary on The Quintessence of Spiritual Practice, The Direct Instructions of the Great Compassionate One, Rangjung Yeshe Publications, pp. 52, 223, {{ISBN|9627341215}}.</ref><ref>Mingyur, Yongey (2014), Turning Confusion into Clarity: A Guide to the Foundation Practices of Tibetan Buddhism, Snow Lion Publications, p. 352, {{ISBN|1611801214}}.</ref> 

慈克秋林仁波切的兩位兒子亦為轉世仁波切：[[達隆噶舉|達隆噶舉]]一系傳承持有者[[帕秋仁波切|帕秋仁波切]]（Phakchok Rinpoche）以及寧瑪派雪謙傳承的[[頂果欽哲仁波切#轉世|頂果欽哲揚希仁波切]]。<ref>Khyentse, Dilgo (2010), Brilliant Moon: The Autobiography of Dilgo Khyentse, Shambhala Publications, p. 198 (all of Chapter 13), {{ISBN|1590307631}}.</ref>

